# Copilot Configuration Instructions

## Project Overview
- **Project**: Department of Sociology & Anthropology Website (SocHub.UCC)
- **Tech Stack**: HTML5, CSS3, JavaScript (ES6+)
- **Deployment**: GitHub Pages
- **URL**: https://den-cpu-dev.github.io/SocHub.UCC/

## Key Files
- `index.html` - Main landing page with hero carousel
- `postgraduate.html` - Postgraduate programs page
- `sandwich.html` - Sandwich program page
- `styles.css` - Global styling with CSS variables
- `script.js` - Interactive features and carousels
- `soasa-emblem.svg` - Department emblem

## Development Guidelines

### Code Standards
- Use semantic HTML5 elements
- Maintain consistent indentation (4 spaces)
- Follow CSS variable naming conventions
- Use ES6+ features (arrow functions, const/let)
- Implement accessibility features (ARIA labels, skip links, keyboard navigation)

### Accessibility Requirements
- All interactive elements must be keyboard accessible
- Include skip navigation links
- Use semantic HTML (nav, header, section, main, footer)
- Add ARIA labels to buttons and icons
- Ensure color contrast meets WCAG AA standards
- Test with screen readers

### Performance Considerations
- Lazy load images (loading="lazy")
- Use event debouncing for resize listeners
- Minify CSS and JavaScript
- Optimize images (WebP format when possible)
- Passive event listeners for scroll/touch

### Security
- Content Security Policy headers configured
- No inline script execution
- Sanitize user inputs
- Use rel="noopener noreferrer" for external links
- Never commit sensitive data

## Common Tasks

### Adding New Pages
1. Create HTML file with semantic structure
2. Include header with navigation
3. Add carousel if needed (use existing hero-carousel pattern)
4. Maintain consistent styling via styles.css
5. Test responsive design at breakpoints: 768px, 1024px

### Modifying Carousels
- Carousel buttons: `.carousel-btn` with z-index: 5
- Keep buttons OUTSIDE carousel-container (not inside)
- Use simple arrow symbols (< >) or proper Unicode arrows
- Test both desktop and mobile

### Updating Styles
- Use CSS variables for colors (--primary-green, --accent-green, etc.)
- Maintain responsive breakpoints (480px, 768px, 1024px, 1400px)
- Always include focus states for accessibility
- Test dark mode compatibility

### JavaScript Functions
- Wrap functions in IIFE to avoid global scope pollution
- Use event delegation for dynamic content
- Include keyboard navigation (Arrow keys, Enter, Escape)
- Add both click and touch support for mobile

## Deployment
- Automatic deployment to GitHub Pages on push to main
- Check `.github/workflows` for deployment config
- Site goes live at https://den-cpu-dev.github.io/SocHub.UCC/

## Contact Form
- Form submission currently simulated (uses setTimeout)
- Ready for backend integration at /api/contact endpoint
- Remove setTimeout once backend is ready

## Known Issues to Address
1. Form submission backend integration needed
2. Test coverage (Jest + Cypress recommended)
3. Phone number placeholder needs real department number
4. Consider build tooling (Vite/Parcel) for production

